#=============================================================================
# Function: configure_arr_apps
# Description: Configure all *arr applications
#
# Sets up Sonarr, Radarr, Readarr, Lidarr with download client and paths.
#
# Arguments:
#   None
#
# Returns:
#   0 - Configuration successful
#   1 - Configuration failed
#
# Example:
